{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_01_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 ダンスを始めたきっかけ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（休憩中、俺は録画していたテレビ番組を観ていた）\n（いろんな業界のプロを取り上げることで人気の番組だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I watch a recorded TV show during break time.)\n(This popular show features professionals from different fields.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3000.000000000001,
          "startTime": 8.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\n自主練終わったので、レッスンルームの鍵を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m done with practice‚ {user}-san.\nHere’s the key to the lesson room…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.96431996629045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "何してるんですか？\n仕事……サボりですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you doing?\nAre you… slacking off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.292698383331302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "違うって。業界のプロの仕事を紹介する番組だよ\n仕事に活かせる内容も多いんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ this is a show that looks at the jobs of professionals in different fields.\nThere’s a lot of information that can be applied to my own work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……ドキュメンタリー番組ですか。疑ってすみません\nちなみに、どんな人を取材してるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So you’re watching a documentary show. Sorry for calling you out.\nWhat’s this episode about‚ by the way?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.70416228105357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今回はプロの女性ダンサーを取材しているらしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re interviewing a professional dancer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.59967871997125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "プロの……ダンサー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A professional… dancer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.39967871997124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "隣、失礼しますっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mind if I join you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.133012053304576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "あ……このダンサーさん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… It’s her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.26938390427198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "知ってるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.981674191289805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "有名な人ですよ\n世界大会で優勝したこともあるベテランです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s a famous dancer.\nA former world champion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "海外のオーディションを突破して\n有名なテーマパークのパレードにも出演していました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s also performed for parades at a world-famous theme park\nwith a really selective audition process.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.34357131150064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "……私、この人のパフォーマンスを\n見たことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve seen her…\nperform in person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.70956825426532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……今もずっと、最前線で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… She’s still actively performing at the highest level…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.78302890654334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（偶然にも、怜が影響を受けたダンサーらしい）\n（俺は黙って怜とともに番組を観ることにした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Coincidentally‚ the featured dancer influenced Rei.)\n(The two of us sit together quietly and watch the rest of the episode.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.96636223987667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "面白かったな\n怜も参考になる話が多かったんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that was interesting.\nYou must’ve found it informative‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.38128071092069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ダンサーの世界では凄く有名な人ですからね\n私自身、目標にしている一人です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ she’s a superstar in the world of dance.\nShe’s one of the people whom I aspire to be like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.22699369845259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "以前、テーマパークのパレードで\n踊ってるのを見たことがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw her perform at the theme park parade\nthat I mentioned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.25460739517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "その時のダンスが印象に残ってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It made a deep impression on me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.12606883594697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "体の動きも、表情も……いえ、指先までもが\n何もかもかっこいいと思えたダンスで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her movements‚ her expression‚ all the way to her fingertips…\nIt was such an impressive dance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.02606883594696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "何より、いつもすっごく楽しそうに踊るんです\nパレードのダンスも、普段のも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More than anything‚ she always looks like she thoroughly enjoys dancing‚\nwhether it’s dancing for parades or elsewhere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそうにか。インタビューでも言ってたな。ただ踊る\nだけがダンスじゃない。表現するのがダンスなんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Enjoys dancing‚ huh? She did mention in the interview\nthat dancing isn’t just about moving your feet; it’s about expression.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.50806435494924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "はい……指先も含めた全身の動きと表情で\n「楽しい」を表現し、伝えようとしている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. She uses her whole body to express her joy‚\nfrom her facial expressions all the way to her fingertips.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "そういう所が、本当に……\n私の憧れで、目標でもあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what I really respect about her\nand why I aspire to be like her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.30173790205825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "あの……{user}さん？\n何をそんなにうなずいてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… {user}-san?\nWhy are you nodding like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "きっとこの人のダンスを見たことが、怜が踊りに\n興味を持ったきっかけなんだろうな……て思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking that she must have been the catalyst\nfor you becoming interested in dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.4405345531158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "きっかけ……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Catalyst?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.27386788644912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。誰でもあるだろ、そういうの\n何かを始めたきっかけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everybody has someone like that‚ don’t they?\nA catalyst for them to get into something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.10014908431492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "……どうなんでしょう。私は\nただ認めてもらうためだけに、ダンスを続けてきて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not sure…\nI only kept dancing to earn the approval of those around me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.92794457264245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……でもそれって\nどちらかというと目的じゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… but if we’re talking about that‚\nwouldn’t it be more appropriate to call that your “goal”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.1628997514957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_01_02-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "目的……？",
